5. **Constraint Check:** Ensure that the "optimal-delta" window (-0.5 to -1.5 eV) is treated as a soft target rather than a hard cutoff, as the sensitivity analysis (Step 2) will provide the necessary context to adjust this range based on the confidence intervals of the DFT data.

The plan is now sufficiently detailed and scientifically rigorous. No further major structural changes are required.
